article_title: New Research Says RomneyCare Worked, ObamaCare Will

article_metadata.description: While critics of the Affordable Care Act use the problems of a newly launched website to discredit the law and the idea of expanded access to healthcare, new evidence keeps emerging of the benefits that expanding access to health coverage.
article_metadata.author: Rob Waters
